trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of drawings that can be operated upon as a single drawing.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av tegninger som kan være styrt av som en enkelt tegning.

trans-unit.source: Use a DrawingGroup to combine multiple drawings into a single, composite drawing.
trans-unit.target: Bruk en DrawingGroup for å kombinere flere tegninger til en enkelt, sammensatt tegning.

trans-unit.source: Unlike other <xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> objects, you can apply a <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.Transform%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.BitmapEffect%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.Opacity%2A> setting, <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.OpacityMask%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.ClipGeometry%2A>, or a <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.GuidelineSet%2A> to a DrawingGroup.
trans-unit.target: I motsetning til andre <xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing>objekter, kan du bruke en <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.Transform%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.BitmapEffect%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.Opacity%2A>innstillingen må du <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.OpacityMask%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.ClipGeometry%2A>, eller <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.GuidelineSet%2A>til en DrawingGroup.</xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.GuidelineSet%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.ClipGeometry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.OpacityMask%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.Opacity%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.BitmapEffect%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup.Transform%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing>

trans-unit.source: The flexibility of this class enables you to create complex scenes.
trans-unit.target: Fleksibilitet til denne klassen kan du opprette sammensatte bakgrunnen.

trans-unit.source: Because DrawingGroup is also a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing>, it can contain other DrawingGroup objects.
trans-unit.target: Fordi DrawingGroup også er en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing>, den kan inneholde andre DrawingGroup-objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing>

trans-unit.source: For more information about <xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> objects, see [Drawing Objects Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om <xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing>objekter, se [tegning oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing>

trans-unit.source: **Freezable Features:** Because it inherits from the <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> class, the DrawingGroup class provides several special features: DrawingGroup objects can be declared as , shared among multiple objects, made read-only to improve performance, cloned, and made thread-safe.
trans-unit.target: **Freezable funksjoner:** fordi den arver fra den <xref:System.Windows.Freezable>klassen klassen DrawingGroup inneholder flere spesielle funksjoner: DrawingGroup objekter kan være deklarert som delt mellom flere objekter, skrivebeskyttet å forbedre ytelsen, klone og gjort sikker.</xref:System.Windows.Freezable>

trans-unit.source: For more information about the different features provided by <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> objects, see [Freezable Objects Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
